{"tid":677603,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"原定下年上映《變形金剛7》遭電影公司抽走","createTime":"2018-05-25T10:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T10:12:24.000Z","uid":42804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c139d6a81ec7ad5b7dc98063098e6835bc0f5927","tid":677603,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180525&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58233065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180525%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58233065&d=gvs1vTaRVkW12O5edArQ4DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=58714d27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180525%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D58233065&h=0b9a5247\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180525&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=58233065</a><br />\n<br />\n由派拉蒙電影公司(Paramount Pictures)拍攝嘅大作《變形金剛》（Transformers）系列一向係其手上嘅王牌，然而最近電影公司卻宣佈，取消原定於下年6月28號上映嘅《變形金剛7》。電影公司會繼續如期於今年12月21號上映「大黃蜂」獨立電影，並被視為系列中嘅《變形金剛6》。<br />\n<br />\n據指電影公司會以喜劇《Limited Partners》取代《變形金剛7》於6月尾上畫，有指抽走嘅決定，可能同上集《變形金剛：終極戰士》（Transformers: The Last Knight）於美國本土票房未如理想有關。"},{"pid":"0cbd3b885e479490262b00dfc709a4ca10f7be43","tid":677603,"uid":42726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"幾時正式收皮？？"},{"pid":"d14cd58e7cdb89f2c4615ad60ac83f6bf15976aa","tid":677603,"uid":186784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T03:15:21.000Z","msg":"自從奶完共之後成套野低質哂 明明頭幾套都好睇 一去到班人打到香港加飲蒙牛個到就真係on99 睇完個集之後就冇再睇過變形金鋼系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3cc5808f2d6a387830618cf66f3da0ac9eab03","tid":677603,"uid":46631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T08:18:01.000Z","msg":"期待緊唔係米高悲拍既變型金剛<br />\n點知唔拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ef6938aa6ca702583ef6a07059efdbadaafd6c","tid":677603,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"沒辦法了，向中央求援吧"},{"pid":"7d5562fba78714014b745e3afb019961518d04a3","tid":677603,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T10:12:24.000Z","msg":"套戲如早一兩集衝出地球玩宇宙就有得延落去既<br />\n<br />\n外星來襲條僑變形金剛救世用足6集真係抵撚死"}]}